1
00:00:00,170 --> 00:00:02,330
Thank you for telling me.

2
00:00:02,330 --> 00:00:02,960
But...

3
00:00:02,960 --> 00:00:04,080
I'm sorry!

4
00:00:04,080 --> 00:00:05,670
I can't go out with you.

5
00:00:05,710 --> 00:00:07,210
W-why?

6
00:00:08,080 --> 00:00:09,170
I've been watching you every day.

7
00:00:09,170 --> 00:00:11,170
I know you better than anyone, Reika.

8
00:00:11,170 --> 00:00:11,790
So...

9
00:00:11,960 --> 00:00:13,000
I'm sorry.

10
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:16,380
Is it my face?
Is it because I'm ugly?

11
00:00:17,040 --> 00:00:20,040
No, that's not it.
There's someone else I like.

12
00:00:21,330 --> 00:00:22,330
So...

13
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:24,750
There's just no way
I can return your feelings.

14
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:27,580
I should go now.

15
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:30,040
So it is my face.

16
00:00:31,420 --> 00:00:33,960
It's my face, my face, my face...

17
00:00:34,130 --> 00:00:35,830
No, I told you it's not!

18
00:00:35,830 --> 00:00:36,830
It is my face!

19
00:00:37,420 --> 00:00:38,960
I'm ugly.

20
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:43,670
Fine, then.

21
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,000
Then I'll ruin your face too!

22
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:47,380
I'll ruin your face!

23
00:00:57,250 --> 00:00:58,580
Sami!!

24
00:00:58,750 --> 00:01:00,630
Why! Why!

25
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:02,460
Help me!
